# RAG Workspace - Collaborative Document Intelligence Platform

## Overview

RAG Workspace is a modern, collaborative document intelligence platform that enables teams to upload, share, and query documents using AI-powered semantic search and chat capabilities. Built on a workspace-based architecture, the application allows multiple users to collaborate on shared document collections with role-based access control.

